887
01:22:30,890 --> 01:22:34,485
Thank you for telling me the truth.

888
01:22:45,237 --> 01:22:49,834
Igarashi, I still wish I was more like you.

889
01:22:53,079 --> 01:22:54,774
Thank you for everything.

890
01:24:05,484 --> 01:24:11,548
