skipping over a pedestrian crossing?"

1030
01:41:09,375 --> 01:41:13,005
He looked so happy when he smiled.

1031
01:41:17,083 --> 01:41:22,988
But...he said there was something
he forgot to say to you.

1032
01:41:24,123 --> 01:41:25,488
